@startuml post_sequence
Title Posts Flow: User creates, edits, and resolves items

/' Participants '/
actor "user: User" as U
participant "page: Home/Posts" as UI
participant "controller: ItemsRoutes" as API
participant "database: ItemModel" as Store

== Load recent items ==

U -> UI : openHome()
activate UI
UI -> API : GET /api/items (optionally status=open)
activate API
API -> API : verifyTokenIfPresent(token)
API -> Store : findRecentItems()
activate Store
Store --> API : List<Item>
deactivate Store
API --> UI : 200 OK (items)
deactivate API
UI -> U : showRecentItems(items)
deactivate UI

== Create a new post ==

U -> UI : click "Report an item"
activate UI
UI -> UI : validate form fields
UI -> API : POST /api/items {title, description, category, image}
activate API
API -> API : verifyToken(token)
API -> API : validateItemPayload()
API -> Store : createItem(userId, payload)
activate Store
Store --> API : newItem
deactivate Store
API --> UI : 201 Created (newItem)
deactivate API
UI -> UI : add item to list
UI -> U : show success message
deactivate UI

== Edit an existing post ==

U -> UI : open my post detail
activate UI
UI -> API : GET /api/items/{id}
activate API
API -> API : verifyToken(token)
API -> Store : getItem(id)
activate Store
Store --> API : item
deactivate Store
API -> API : checkOwnership(userId, item)
alt Not Owner
  API --> UI : 403 Forbidden
else Owner
  API --> UI : 200 OK (item)
end
activate UI
UI -> UI : edit fields
UI -> API : PUT /api/items/{id} {updated fields}
activate API
API -> API : verifyToken(token)
API -> API : validateItemPayload()
API -> Store : updateItem(id, payload)
activate Store
Store --> API : updatedItem
deactivate Store
API --> UI : 200 OK (updatedItem)
deactivate API
UI -> UI : refresh item in list
UI -> U : show updated item
deactivate UI

== Mark a post as resolved ==

U -> UI : markResolved(id)
activate UI
UI -> API : POST /api/items/{id}/resolve
activate API
API -> API : verifyToken(token)
API -> Store : getItem(id)
activate Store
Store --> API : item
deactivate Store
API -> API : checkOwnership(userId, item)
alt Not Owner
  API --> UI : 403 Forbidden
else Owner
  API -> Store : markResolved(id)
  activate Store
  Store --> API : resolvedItem
  deactivate Store
  API --> UI : 200 OK (resolvedItem)
end
deactivate API
UI -> UI : update status to resolved
UI -> U : show resolved state

deactivate UI
@enduml
